{"type": "article", "id": 17373, "title": "OFF-WHITE “Blue Collar”系列单鞋", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-11T06:34:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607103928wHGO46hAMyVuBrlT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tOFF-WHITE 是黑人设计师 Virgil Abloh 在 2014 年创办的品牌，有地道的街头时尚风格。他们最新推出的是 2016 年春夏系列“Blue Collar”，有四种配色：黑白条纹，迷彩，纯白和黑色的深浅条纹，既有适合大众的简约款式，也有极具视觉冲击和品牌辨识度的。鞋身均为皮革，在后跟处分别标注了“OFF”和“WHITE”的黑体字。目前已开始预售，迷彩款售价 321 欧元，其余售价 299 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.antonioli.eu/en/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&amp;q=Blue+Collar&amp;gender=men\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144455lcb1uDjTJ6Y2UAFr.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"627\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144456aobI6UGWzcx0mnE5.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"626\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66595745\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144456lJdzETxZQwcki8p2.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"627\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144457OIpzu4lc30a27RXt.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"627\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144457p5dNbyOK38GwEXsz.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"627\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144458rkCERY5nd70PvXKs.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"627\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726